&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;关注 Michael：&lt;a href="https://x.com/mbrkhrdt" rel="noreferrer noopener" target="_blank"&gt;X/Twitter&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href="https://bsky.app/profile/michaelb.nyc" rel="noreferrer noopener" target="_blank"&gt;Bluesky&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href="https://instagram.com/m.brkhrdt" rel="noreferrer noopener" target="_blank"&gt;Instagram&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
